{"tid":445333,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"去應酬時，老闆摸我背脊...","createTime":"2017-10-23T09:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T14:53:35.000Z","uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":104,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd45fe96b83070dee0aa3b0b7bbe4ed1bc34d78","tid":445333,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"因為公司有一個重要既晚宴，老闆叫出席既員工都著得靚啲，所以我就著左一條大露背既連身裙，冇露胸既，保守得黎有點性感，同埋我覺得我背脊係最靚，所以我都幾鍾意條裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但當晚出席時，老闆唔知係咪已經飲大左，一見到我就好興奮咁抱住我，我果下已經有d想推開佢，點知佢摟到實一實，仲話帶我去見d大客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我見有大客見，都唔好發作，佢隻手就一路放落我背脊到，係掂到實一實，有衫都算，但我果日係著大露背呀!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老闆仲要笑淫淫咁，感覺好似抽水，但我又要對住d客，唔敢講d咩，最尾講完，我就即刻話去廁所先解脫到..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最慘係同男朋友講時，佢話呢d好平常，係西方社會既社交禮儀喎，話返我轉頭添...<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92323325b402e70c8a573cb72a9d7e3ff87c1e4b","tid":445333,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"lindoff 唔係丹麥既咩"},{"pid":"232144861bda0e6715fb4ff978395e8d592e5438","tid":445333,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lindoff 唔係丹麥既咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 丹你老母咩"},{"pid":"031a7967eb57020b74c049810a28ee8088a78f1c","tid":445333,"uid":41508,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0093d06e9fd57773a26c1fcdf59f67d5537ceffc","tid":445333,"uid":36696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:47:51.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7489b40bb9ad203a89bde641f9925e4dfa2bd6c","tid":445333,"uid":